name: R5_v3_HumanActSite_for_R4
title: Cross-version VS for R5.HumanActSite for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents concepts from http://terminology.hl7.org/ValueSet/v3-HumanActSite|2.0.0 for use in FHIR R4. Concepts not present here have direct `equivalent` mappings crossing all versions from R5 to R4.
